Package: eirm
Type: Package
Title: Explanatory Item Response Modeling for Dichotomous and Polytomous Items
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Okan Bulut <bulut@ualberta.ca>
Maintainer: Okan Bulut <bulut@ualberta.ca>
Description: Analysis of dichotomous and polytomous response data using the explanatory item response modeling framework (De Boeck & Wilson (2004) <doi:10.1007/978-1-4757-3990-9>). Generalized linear mixed modeling is used for examining the effects of item-related and person-related variables on item responses. 
Depends:
    lme4,
    reshape2,
    optimx
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
